      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just about the money. it's the fact that i built this whole identity around being the guy who makes things happen. now i'm just the guy who ruined everything for everyone. i feel like there's no way to ever fix this reputation, or even live with the shame of it. it feels like there's no real path forward where i'm not just a walking embarrassment.",
